# Auto-Graded Quiz Generator with Ollama

![Project Banner](https://via.placeholder.com/800x200?text=Auto-Graded+Quiz+Generator)

An AI-powered application that generates quizzes from textbooks/notes and automatically grades responses using Ollama's local LLMs.

## Features

- 📄 Extract text from PDF documents
- ❓ Generate 20 quiz questions (15 MCQs + 5 True/False) with explanations
- ✅ Auto-grade user responses with detailed feedback
- 🏠 Runs locally with Ollama (no API keys needed)
- 💾 Save/Load quizzes in JSON format
- 🌐 Streamlit web interface

## Tech Stack

- **Backend**: Python, Flask
- **Frontend**: Streamlit
- **AI**: Ollama (Llama 3/Mistral), LangChain
- **PDF Processing**: PyPDF2

## Prerequisites

- Python 3.8+
- Ollama installed ([installation guide](https://ollama.ai/))
- At least one Ollama model (e.g., `llama3`)

## Installation

1. Clone the repository:
   ```bash
   git clone https://github.com/yourusername/quiz-generator.git
   cd quiz-generator





python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Linux/Mac
# or
venv\Scripts\activate    # Windows

